    <item>
      <title>托克承认其创始人克劳德·多芬批准行贿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trafigura-admits-its-founder-claude-dauphin-approved-bribes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大宗商品贸易巨头托克集团 (Trafigura Group) 承认，其创始人兼前首席执行官克劳德·多芬 (Claude Dauphin) 批准了巴西石油交易的贿赂行为，这是该行业的老板首次卷入美国一系列广泛的腐败案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/trafigura-admits-its-founder-claude-dauphin-approved-bribes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 15:52:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
